Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.57,0:22:27.91,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}いつかの願いは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.08,0:22:32.37,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}土の中で眠って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.58,0:22:41.63,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}約束の時刻に 希望の根が出るんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.76,0:22:45.64,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}二人が出会った頃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.64,0:22:50.68,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}夢など まだだめだった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.77,0:22:54.61,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}どれくらい時が過ぎ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.69,0:23:00.07,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}花は咲くのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.90,0:23:05.37,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}この涙を君に捧ぐ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.37,0:23:09.83,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}もっと君が輝くなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.95,0:23:15.42,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}ずっと見守ってた沈默の空から
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.42,0:23:20.05,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}今 僕は雨になろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.42,0:23:23.51,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}あぁ 君に捧ぐ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.51,0:23:28.14,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}こんな僕に出来ることは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.14,0:23:33.27,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}キミの虚しさを少しでも癒すこと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.35,0:23:38.61,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}さぁ 僕は雨になろう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.57,0:22:27.91,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}不知何時的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.08,0:22:32.37,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}沉睡在土壤中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.58,0:22:41.63,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}在約定好的時間 萌生出希望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.76,0:22:45.64,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}當兩人相遇之時
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.64,0:22:50.68,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}夢想還不成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.77,0:22:54.61,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}不知要過多長時間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.69,0:23:00.07,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}花才會綻放呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.90,0:23:05.37,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}把這顆眼淚獻給你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.37,0:23:09.83,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}如果你能夠更加閃耀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.95,0:23:15.42,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}我會從一直看著你的沉默的天空中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.42,0:23:20.05,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}成雨落下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.42,0:23:23.51,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}啊 獻給你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.51,0:23:28.14,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}我所能做到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.14,0:23:33.27,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}就是輕輕撫慰空虛的你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.35,0:23:38.61,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}來吧 我將成為雨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-----------ED-----------
